       *   //this:
       *   when(mock.foo()).thenReturn(1, 2, 3);
       *
       *   //is equivalent to:
       *   when(mock.foo()).thenAnswer(AdditionalAnswers.returnsElementsOf(Arrays.asList(1, 2, 3)));
       * </code></pre>
